The task is to identify and extract the line item and value that represents the decrease in amounts owed to the entity for goods or services sold or provided on credit. This corresponds to the change in "Accounts Receivable" on the cash flow statement, since accounts receivable tracks amounts owed by customers.

From the given cash flow statement, the relevant line is:

| (Increase) Decrease in Accounts Receivable  | -10537836.59 | 2024-02-05 |

This line represents the net change in amounts owed to the entity for goods or services sold on credit during the period.

Hence, the value to extract is "-10537836.59".

```json
{"solution": {"value": "-10537836.59"}}
```
